Zcash Ecosystem Digest – Week of June 28, 2026

### Shielded Labs, ZODL, Zcash Foundation Updates

## Shielded Labs

1. Ironwood Proposal for Zcash

Shielded Labs announced the Ironwood proposal alongside ZODL, the Zcash Foundation, Tachyon, and Valar Group. Ironwood introduces a new shielded pool designed to strengthen supply verification while preserving Zcash's privacy guarantees following the Orchard vulnerability.

Post: https://x.com/i/status/2063262293442678830

2. Orchard Vulnerability Disclosure

Shielded Labs published a detailed explanation of the Orchard vulnerability, describing how it was discovered, responsibly disclosed, and fixed through a coordinated network upgrade.

Post: https://x.com/i/status/2066329282973249847

